Paper: hep-th/9509010

Date: 1995-09-05

Title: New prescription in light-cone gauge theories

Authors: D.K.Park

Comments: LATEX, 9pages

New prescription for the singularities of light-cone gauge theories issuggested. The new prescription provides Green's function which is identicalwith and different from that of Mandelstam-Leibbrandt prescription at $d=4$ and$d=2$ respectively.